Discovery Proxy for Multicast DNS-Based
Service Discovery
2020", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC8766.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document specifies a network proxy that uses Multicast DNS to automatically populate the wide-area unicast Domain Name System namespace with records describing devices and services found on the local link."];
